Available tissue types

Source: R/available_tissueSiteDeatilIds.R
available_tissueSiteDetailIds.Rd

Returns a character vector of valid Tissue IDs that can be supplied to functions which include the argument tissueSiteDetailId.

Usage

available_tissueSiteDetailIds()

Value

A character vector.

Examples

available_tissueSiteDetailIds()
